-katkisi" class="wp-block-heading">Türkiye&#8217;de Devlet Hastanelerinin Sağlık Hizmetlerine Katkısı</h2>
<div id="chat-history" class="chat-history-scroll-container">
<div id="5537e89d6dc8c22c" class="conversation-container message-actions-hover-boundary ng-star-inserted">
<div class="response-container ng-tns-c4099141682-81 response-container-with-gpi ng-star-inserted response-container-has-multiple-responses">
<div class="presented-response-container ng-tns-c4099141682-81">
