<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Atılım University offers internship and job opportunities through its Career Center, which also organizes “Career Days.” Academic advisors guide students in course selection and career planning. The Psychological Support Unit provides free therapy sessions. The Office for Students with Disabilities ensures accessibility accommodations. The Scholarship Office manages merit- and need-based scholarships. A mentorship program provides guidance and support for new students.</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-12-29T10:47:35Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2025-11-04T10:47:58Z' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'atilim-university';
