n Turkey","publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/atasehir-adiguzel-meslek-yuksekokulu-1.webp","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/atasehir-adiguzel-meslek-yuksekokulu-1.webp","width":"853","height":"479","inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/atasehir-adiguzel-vocational-school/#webpage","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/atasehir-adiguzel-vocational-school/","name":"Ataşehir Adıgüzel Vocational School - RoadtoStudy","datePublished":"2025-11-22T13:41:51+03:00","dateModified":"2025-11-22T13:41:51+03:00","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website"},"primaryImageOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/atasehir-adiguzel-meslek-yuksekokulu-1.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/busra/","name":"busra","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/busra/","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a3c0f700b03ed22f8ab3a40880c2b539035a9a6e21bb16550f65e22a0ff39809?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a3c0f700b03ed22f8ab3a40880c2b539035a9a6e21bb16550f65e22a0ff39809?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","caption":"busra","inLanguage":"en-US"}},{"@type":"Article","headline":"Ataşehir Adıgüzel Vocational School - RoadtoStudy","keywords":"Ataşehir Adıgüzel Vocational School","datePublished":"2025-11-22T13:41:51+03:00","dateModified":"2025-11-22T13:41:51+03:00","author":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/busra/","name":"busra"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"description":"Ataşehir Adıgüzel Vocational School is a foundation vocational school established in 2009 in the Ataşehir district of Istanbul. Prioritizing quality education","name":"Ataşehir Adıgüzel Vocational School - RoadtoStudy","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/atasehir-adiguzel-vocational-school/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/atasehir-adiguzel-vocational-school/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/atasehir-adiguzel-meslek-yuksekokulu-1.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/atasehir-adiguzel-vocational-school/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<h2 class="wp-block-heading">History and Vision</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://www.adiguzel.edu.tr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ataşehir Adıgüzel Vocational School</a> is a foundation vocational school established in 2009 in the Ataşehir district of Istanbul. Prioritizing quality education and practical learning, the school aims to train qualified professionals, particularly in the fields of health, social sciences, and technical disciplines.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The school&#8217;s vision is to prepare students for the professional world through an innovative and sector-oriented education model. With programs that combine theoretical knowledge and practical skills, it stands out as an institution offering both academic and social opportunities thanks to its central location in Istanbul.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Adopting a student-centered educational approach, Ataşehir Adıgüzel Vocational School aims to equip its graduates with the competencies needed to compete in the job market. To support this goal, it establishes strong ties with the business world and provides internship and hands-on training opportunities.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Education</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ataşehir Adıgüzel Vocational School offers a wide range of associate degree programs. Education is provided through academic units such as the Vocational School of Health Services, the Vocational School of Social Sciences, and the Vocational School of Technical Sciences.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkish is the primary language of instruction, although some programs include courses in English. The school is known for its practical education models in health, social sciences, and technical fields, giving students the chance to apply theoretical knowledge in real-world settings.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The academic staff consists of experienced faculty members with sector expertise. The education model that blends theory with practice helps graduates adapt quickly to professional environments. Erasmus+ and other exchange programs offer students international experience opportunities.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Campus and Technological Infrastructure</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Located in Istanbul&#8217;s Ataşehir district, Ataşehir Adıgüzel Vocational School features a modern campus. It includes spacious classrooms, computer labs, health service laboratories, and social areas.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Modern laboratories dedicated to health sciences allow students to develop their practical skills. Well-equipped facilities support programs in health and technical fields. With high-speed internet and digital learning platforms, students can easily access course materials.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The library provides extensive resources in health sciences, social sciences, and technical areas. Students can access both printed and digital materials to support their studies. There are also dedicated spaces for group work.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Accommodation</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ataşehir Adıgüzel Vocational School does not have its own dormitories. However, there are various private dormitories, student residences, and rental apartment options near the campus. Thanks to Istanbul’s central structure, accommodation options are diverse and accessible.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Private dormitories typically offer internet, security, meals, laundry services, and study areas. The school’s International Relations Office provides guidance to students regarding accommodation options.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ataşehir’s student-friendly environment and well-developed transportation network make it easy to find housing. Student dormitories near the campus also offer a transportation advantage.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Social Life</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ataşehir Adıgüzel Vocational School has a dynamic campus culture that supports social activities and student clubs. These clubs promote social responsibility, cultural events, and technical seminars that contribute to students’ personal development.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Annual spring festivals, cultural events, and sports tournaments make campus life more vibrant. Sports halls, fitness centers, and open-air activity areas encourage physical engagement.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ataşehir’s central location and social amenities allow students to take part in various cultural and recreational events outside the campus as well. Shopping malls, art galleries, and cultural events provide students with an integrated urban experience.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">International students can visit the <em>Road to Study</em> platform for more information on university life in Turkey.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Cultural Integration for International Students</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ataşehir Adıgüzel Vocational School places great importance on helping international students adapt. The International Relations Office provides guidance on registration, course selection, visa applications, and residence permits.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Orientation programs offer detailed information about campus life, social activities, Istanbul’s culture, and transportation. These programs help students adjust to university life and Ataşehir’s dynamic environment more quickly.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Student clubs organize social responsibility projects, cultural events, and meet-and-greet activities to help students from different countries connect. Istanbul’s cosmopolitan structure also offers many cultural and social experiences outside the campus. Ataşehir’s central location supports students’ integration into social life.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Health Services and Security</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ataşehir Adıgüzel Vocational School prioritizes student health and safety. The campus has a health unit providing basic medical services and first aid. For more extensive healthcare needs, partnerships with public and private hospitals in Istanbul are in place.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">International students can benefit from public healthcare services in Turkey through the General Health Insurance (GSS) system. The International Relations Office assists students with the insurance application process. Health information sessions are held regularly on campus.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Campus security is ensured by 24/7 personnel and surveillance systems. Entry and exit points are monitored to maintain student safety. Istanbul’s overall security and Ataşehir’s central structure contribute to a peaceful academic environment.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Transportation</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ataşehir Adıgüzel Vocational School is centrally located in Istanbul’s Ataşehir district, offering excellent transportation access. The campus is easily reached via metro, buses, minibuses, and shared taxis. In particular, the Ümraniye–Ataşehir–Göztepe Metro Line and the Kadıköy–Kartal Metro Line provide direct access.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Students can use the IstanbulKart for discounted public transportation. Being close to the city center also makes it easy for students to participate in both academic and social activities. Public transport access to the campus is convenient due to its central location.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The school is approximately 30 km from Sabiha Gökçen Airport and 45 km from Istanbul Airport. Both airports are accessible by public transport or private shuttle services. Direct bus routes are also available from Istanbul’s main bus terminal (Esenler). The extensive transportation network allows students to easily attend social and cultural events throughout the city.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Student Support Services</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ataşehir Adıgüzel Vocational School offers comprehensive services to support students’ academic and personal development. The International Relations Office provides guidance for international students on registration, visa processes, health insurance, and residence permits.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Psychological Counseling and Guidance Center supports students in areas such as adjustment, exam anxiety, stress management, and personal growth. Individual sessions and group activities help ease adaptation and promote mental well-being.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Career Development Center supports students in career planning, job placement, and internships after graduation. Workshops on CV writing, interview techniques, and networking events with industry professionals help students prepare for the job market.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Academic advising services guide students in course selection, exam preparation, and academic success. These services are regularly provided to help students achieve their academic and career goals. Ataşehir Adıgüzel Vocational School offers a wide range of services to support both academic and social development.</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-11-22T10:41:51Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2025-11-04T10:43:01Z' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'atasehir-adiguzel-vocational-school';
