<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Students can use the Trabzon Card for discounted fares on public transportation. Bus stops are conveniently located for easy access. The university also provides shuttle services between campuses.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university is approximately 5 km from Trabzon Airport, accessible by public transport or taxi. There are also direct bus routes from the Trabzon Bus Terminal to the campuses. The central location and robust transport system make commuting easy for students.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Student Support Services</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Avrasya University offers a wide range of services to support academic and personal development. The International Relations Office assists international students with registration, visa applications, health insurance, and residence permits.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Psychological Counseling and Guidance Center provides individual and group support for issues like adaptation, exam stress, and personal growth.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Career Development Center helps students prepare for the workforce with career planning workshops, CV writing sessions, and mock interviews. Through partnerships with local businesses, students can access internship opportunities.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Academic advising offers one-on-one support with course selection, study strategies, and exam preparation. These services aim to enhance academic success and support students in achieving their career goals.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-11-05T14:08:20Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2025-11-04T14:12:51Z') WHERE "collection" = 'pages' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_pages" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'avrasya-university' );
