niversitesi-tanitimi-1.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/antalya-bilim-university/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<h2 class="wp-block-heading">History and Vision</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Antalya Bilim University aims to become a pioneering institution in entrepreneurship and a competitive player on the international stage through its innovative and practice-oriented scientific research and education.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Education</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">With 7 faculties and 4 schools, Antalya Bilim University offers a broad academic range. The faculties include Dentistry, Fine Arts and Architecture, Law, Economics, Administrative and Social Sciences, Engineering and Natural Sciences, Health Sciences, and Tourism. The university offers 19 undergraduate, 16 associate degree, 21 master&#8217;s, and 2 doctoral programs, providing diverse educational opportunities.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Its academic staff consists of experienced and expert faculty members. The university’s educational approach focuses on blending theoretical knowledge with practical application to support students’ professional and personal development.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For more details, please visit the official website of <a href="https://antalya.edu.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Antalya Bilim University</a>.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Campus and Technological Infrastructure</h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="930" height="636" src="https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/campus-and-technological-infrastructure.webp" alt="" class="wp-image-11024" srcset="https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/campus-and-technological-infrastructure.webp 930w, https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/campus-and-technological-infrastructure-300x205.webp 300w, https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/campus-and-technological-infrastructure-768x525.webp 768w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 930px) 100vw, 930px" /></figure>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The campus of Antalya Bilim University is known for its modern and high-tech facilities. The library offers a rich collection and ideal study spaces. Laboratories, workshops, and research centers allow students to improve their practical skills.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university emphasizes sustainability and eco-friendly practices, running various projects on energy efficiency and waste management. High-speed internet access and digital learning platforms are also available throughout the campus.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Student Housing</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Antalya Bilim University provides comfortable and secure accommodation options. The on-campus female dormitory has 87 rooms with a total capacity of 250 students, including 31 single, 51 four-person, and 5 triple rooms.</p>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="768" src="https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/yurtlar-1024x768.webp" alt="" class="wp-image-11026" style="width:512px;height:auto" srcset="https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/yurtlar-1024x768.webp 1024w, https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/yurtlar-300x225.webp 300w, https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/yurtlar-768x576.webp 768w, https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/yurtlar-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/yurtlar.webp 1920w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>
</div>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Rooms are equipped with essentials such as desks, wardrobes, and beds. Shared facilities include kitchens, laundry rooms, study rooms, and lounges. Security services and 24/7 hot water ensure a safe and comfortable environment.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Nearby private dormitories and apartments offer additional accommodation options, catering to different budgets and preferences.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Student Life</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university offers a vibrant social and cultural environment. Student clubs and societies organize events, seminars, and workshops throughout the year, helping students develop their interests and skills.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">On-campus concerts, theater performances, and exhibitions promote participation in the arts. Sports facilities and tournaments support physical activity.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The city of Antalya, with its historical sites, natural beauty, beaches, and dynamic social scene, offers rich experiences outside the campus. Students can join local events, explore the culture, and expand their social circles.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For more information on university life in Turkey, international students can visit the Road to Study platform.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Cultural Adaptation for International Students</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Committed to its international vision, Antalya Bilim University hosts students from various countries. The International Student Office organizes orientation programs, language courses, and cultural events to help international students adapt to university life.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://roadtostudy.com/turkiyede-tomer-turkce-ogretim-merkezleri/" data-type="link" data-id="https://roadtostudy.com/turkiyede-tomer-turkce-ogretim-merkezleri/">TÖMER (Turkish Language and Foreign Languages Application</a> and Research Center) offers Turkish language courses. Additionally, seminars and trips introduce students to Turkish culture and traditions.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Through Erasmus+ and other international exchange programs, students can study or intern abroad, expanding their global perspective and cross-cultural interaction.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Health Services and Security</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The campus health unit provides first-response care and refers students to professional medical centers when needed. Psychological counseling services are also available through expert psychologists.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">A 24/7 security team ensures campus safety. Surveillance cameras monitor the campus, and access is controlled at entry points. Security measures are especially enhanced around dorms and common areas.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university has a comprehensive crisis management plan for emergencies like fires and natural disasters, with regular drills and awareness seminars for students.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Transportation</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Located in Döşemealtı, just 20 minutes from Antalya city center, the campus is easily accessible by public transportation provided by Antalya Metropolitan Municipality. Regular buses and minibuses serve the campus.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university also offers private shuttle services on specific routes, especially during peak hours, ensuring timely and comfortable transportation.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Students use the Antalya Card system for discounted public transport. The city&#8217;s flat terrain and bike-friendly roads make cycling a popular alternative.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Being a coastal city, Antalya also offers sea transport. For intercity and international travel, Antalya Airport provides a major advantage for international students.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Student Support Services</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Antalya Bilim University actively provides various services to support students’ academic and personal development. The Career Planning and Alumni Relations Office helps students set career goals and shares job/internship opportunities. It also offers CV writing, mock interviews, and industry-related events.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Students in financial need can benefit from several scholarship options, including merit-based scholarships, sibling discounts, need-based aid, and scholarships for sports and arts achievements.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university adopts an accessible campus policy for students with disabilities, with physical adaptations, customized academic materials, and personal counseling services to ensure full participation.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Each student is also assigned an academic advisor through the student advising system, offering guidance in both academic and social matters.</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-11-03T10:49:15Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2025-11-03T10:49:15Z' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'antalya-bilim-university';
