Language":"en-US"},{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/ankara-medipol-university.webp","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/ankara-medipol-university.webp","width":"2560","height":"1707","inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ankara-medipol-university/#webpage","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ankara-medipol-university/","name":"Ankara Medipol University - RoadtoStudy","datePublished":"2025-11-01T14:55:34+03:00","dateModified":"2025-11-03T13:18:43+03:00","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website"},"primaryImageOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/ankara-medipol-university.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/busra/","name":"busra","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/busra/","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a3c0f700b03ed22f8ab3a40880c2b539035a9a6e21bb16550f65e22a0ff39809?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a3c0f700b03ed22f8ab3a40880c2b539035a9a6e21bb16550f65e22a0ff39809?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","caption":"busra","inLanguage":"en-US"}},{"@type":"Article","headline":"Ankara Medipol University - RoadtoStudy","keywords":"Ankara Medipol University","datePublished":"2025-11-01T14:55:34+03:00","dateModified":"2025-11-03T13:18:43+03:00","author":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/busra/","name":"busra"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"description":"Ankara Medipol University is a foundation university established in Ankara in 2018. Founded by the Medipol Education Health and Research Foundation, the","name":"Ankara Medipol University - RoadtoStudy","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ankara-medipol-university/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ankara-medipol-university/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/ankara-medipol-university.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ankara-medipol-university/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<h2 class="wp-block-heading">History and Vision of the University</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://www.ankaramedipol.edu.tr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ankara Medipol University</a> is a foundation university established in Ankara in 2018. Founded by the Medipol Education Health and Research Foundation, the university quickly gained attention with its education model focused on health and technology. Recognized as one of Turkey’s specialized institutions in health sciences, Ankara Medipol combines an innovative educational approach with a modern campus infrastructure.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university’s vision is to become a globally respected educational institution in the fields of health sciences and engineering. By applying innovative teaching methods and hands-on learning models, it aims to equip students with the skills needed to compete globally and thrive both academically and professionally.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Through an interdisciplinary education approach, Ankara Medipol University focuses on developing both the theoretical knowledge and practical skills of its students. The academic staff consists of experienced and expert faculty members in health sciences and engineering.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Education</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ankara Medipol University offers a wide range of undergraduate, graduate, and doctoral programs. The university houses various academic units, including the Faculty of Medicine, Faculty of Dentistry, Faculty of Pharmacy, Faculty of Health Sciences, and Faculty of Engineering and Natural Sciences.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Courses are offered in both English and Turkish. An English preparatory program is available for international students. Practical training is a key component of education in health sciences, with students benefiting from access to advanced laboratory facilities.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university participates in Erasmus+ and other exchange programs, providing students with opportunities to study and intern abroad. Clinical training, internships, and project-based learning help students prepare for their professional careers after graduation.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Campus and Technological Infrastructure</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Located in central areas of Ankara, Ankara Medipol University offers a modern and comfortable educational environment. Campuses include spacious classrooms, high-tech laboratories, modern simulation centers, and digital library services.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Its strong focus on health sciences provides students with extensive hands-on learning opportunities. Anatomy labs, simulation centers, and clinical training spaces in the Faculty of Health Sciences allow students to apply their theoretical knowledge in practice.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university library offers a vast collection of printed and digital resources. Students can easily access academic materials through the online library system. High-speed internet is available campus-wide, enabling access to digital learning platforms and online course materials.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Accommodation</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ankara Medipol University does not have its own dormitories. However, numerous private dormitories and student apartments are located near campus. These accommodations are typically equipped with internet, security, dining services, laundry facilities, and study rooms.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Thanks to the university’s central location, students have access to a wide range of housing options in the city. Nearby private dormitories offer a safe and comfortable living environment at reasonable costs. International students can receive assistance from the International Relations Office regarding accommodation and dormitory applications.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There are also many rental apartments available around the campus. Ankara’s student-friendly environment and central location make it easier for students to find suitable housing.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Social Life</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ankara Medipol University has a vibrant campus life that supports social activities and cultural engagement. Student clubs organize scientific events, cultural workshops, and sports activities that enrich campus life.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Annual spring festivals, cultural celebrations, and social responsibility projects provide opportunities for students to enjoy themselves while developing social skills. The university’s sports facilities encourage students to stay physically active.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Its central location in Ankara gives students easy access to various social and cultural events. Museums, theaters, and other public venues offer students a meaningful way to spend their free time. International students interested in learning more about university life in Turkey can visit the Road to Study platform.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Cultural Adaptation for International Students</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">With its multicultural environment and health-focused academic programs, Ankara Medipol University places great emphasis on helping international students adapt. The International Relations Office guides students through processes such as registration, course selection, visa applications, and residence permits.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Orientation programs provide detailed information about campus life, transportation, social activities, and academic procedures. These initiatives help new students quickly adjust to university life and life in Ankara.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Student clubs organize cultural events, social projects, and technical seminars that foster interaction among students from different countries. Ankara’s multicultural structure and dynamic urban life help international students adapt to the local culture more easily.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Health Services and Safety</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ankara Medipol University prioritizes the health and safety of its students. The campus health center offers basic medical care and first aid support. For more comprehensive health services, students are referred to public and private hospitals in Ankara.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">International students can benefit from Turkey’s General Health Insurance (GSS) system to access public healthcare at affordable rates. The International Relations Office assists students with the health insurance application process. The university also organizes regular health awareness seminars and informative events.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Campus security is maintained 24/7 with personnel and camera surveillance systems. Entry and exit points are monitored, and security measures are strictly enforced. Ankara’s overall safety and the campus’s central location ensure a secure educational environment for students.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Transportation</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ankara Medipol University offers convenient access due to its location near the city center. Students can easily reach the campus via buses, minibuses, and the metro. The Ankara Metro Network provides efficient access to areas surrounding the campus.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Students benefit from discounted fares on public transport with the AnkaraKart. Being near the city center helps students save time on commuting. Bus stops and metro links around the campus offer easy access to various parts of the city.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university is about 30 kilometers from Esenboğa Airport and can be reached by bus or taxi. There are also direct bus services from Ankara’s main bus terminal (AŞTİ) to the campus. Its central location makes commuting both within and outside the city easy for students.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Student Support Services</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ankara Medipol University offers a broad range of support services to aid students in their academic and personal development. The International Relations Office provides individual guidance on registration, visa procedures, <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/en/student-health-insurance-options-in-turkey/" data-type="link" data-id="https://roadtostudy.com/en/student-health-insurance-options-in-turkey/">health insurance</a>, and residence permits.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Psychological Counseling and Guidance Center supports students in managing adaptation challenges, exam anxiety, stress, and personal development. One-on-one sessions and group activities help promote mental well-being and ease the adjustment process.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Career Development Center prepares students for the job market by organizing workshops on career planning, job search strategies, and interview simulations. Career days and networking events with industry representatives help students build professional connections.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Academic advisory services offer one-on-one guidance throughout students’ academic journeys—from course selection to graduation. These services aim to enhance academic success and help students achieve their career goals. With this multi-faceted support system, Ankara Medipol University helps students grow both academically and personally.</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-11-01T11:55:34Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2025-11-03T10:18:43Z' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'ankara-medipol-university';
