<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Academic advisory services offer one-on-one guidance throughout students’ academic journeys—from course selection to graduation. These services aim to enhance academic success and help students achieve their career goals. With this multi-faceted support system, Ankara Medipol University helps students grow both academically and personally.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-11-01T11:55:34Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2025-11-03T10:18:43Z') WHERE "collection" = 'pages' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_pages" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'ankara-medipol-university' );
