ra Hacı Bayram Veli University - RoadtoStudy","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ankara-haci-bayram-veli-university/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ankara-haci-bayram-veli-university/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/ankara-haci-bayram-veli-universitesi-akademik-kadro-ilani_68e82e2bd7ced.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ankara-haci-bayram-veli-university/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<h2 class="wp-block-heading">History and Vision of the University</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://www.ahbv.edu.tr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ankara Hacı Bayram Veli University</a> is a public university established in 2018 following the separation of certain faculties from Gazi University. Located in Turkey&#8217;s capital, Ankara, the university has a strong background in education, culture, and the arts. Named after Hacı Bayram Veli, the university aims to blend the traditional values of knowledge and wisdom with modern academic approaches.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Its vision is to cultivate innovative, socially engaged individuals with high scientific productivity and strong ethical values. With a focus on social sciences, humanities, arts, and cultural studies, the university aspires to become an internationally recognized center of education.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Committed to student-centered learning, the university fosters creative and research-oriented individuals who contribute to society. Its interdisciplinary structure and location in a major hub of science and culture like Ankara strengthen students&#8217; academic development.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Education</h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img decoding="async" src="https://hacibayram.edu.tr/api/files/1/Hac%C4%B1bayram%20AHBV/hukuk%28tr-TR%29/ana%20sayfa%20foto%C4%9Fraf%C4%B1/20140603_110414.jpg" alt="Image"/></figure>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ankara Hacı Bayram Veli University adopts an education model focused on social sciences and the arts. The university comprises faculties such as Literature, Economics and Administrative Sciences, Fine Arts, Law, and Tourism.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkish is the primary language of instruction, though some programs offer courses in English. International students can optionally attend a Turkish preparatory program. Through Erasmus+ and other exchange programs, students have opportunities to study abroad.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The academic staff includes experts with national and international experience. The curriculum integrates theoretical knowledge with practical applications. Students can participate in research projects, workshops, and social responsibility initiatives to enhance their professional skills.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Campus and Technological Infrastructure</h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img decoding="async" src="https://hacibayram.edu.tr/api/files/1/Hac%C4%B1bayram%20AHBV/hukuk%28tr-TR%29/ana%20sayfa%20foto%C4%9Fraf%C4%B1/3.jpg" alt="Image"/></figure>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university has a wide campus network spread across various parts of Ankara. The central campus, located in the city center, offers convenient access. Facilities include modern classrooms, lecture halls, laboratories, libraries, and social spaces.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Emphasizing technological infrastructure, the university provides access to digital course materials and online academic resources. Students can follow their academic progress through digital platforms, with high-speed internet available throughout the campus.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Studios, workshops, and exhibition areas in the arts faculties support hands-on education. Technical facilities are especially well-developed in the Fine Arts and Tourism faculties. Research centers and labs contribute significantly to academic productivity.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Student Housing</h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.esenbogayildirimbeyazitogrenciyurdu.com.tr/assets/images/product/product/dis-cephe-1.jpg" alt="Image"/></figure>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university does not have its own dormitories. However, Ankara offers various accommodation options. KYK dormitories, run by the Ministry of Youth and Sports, are widely available and provide affordable housing for students.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Private dormitories and student apartments are located near campus areas and offer amenities such as security, internet, meals, laundry, and social spaces. The university provides guidance on accommodation, especially for students coming from outside the city.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">International students can receive support from the International Relations Office during the housing process. Living costs in Ankara are generally more affordable than in other major cities, offering budget-friendly accommodation options.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Social Life</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university has an active student community that promotes a vibrant social life. Student clubs organize cultural events, artistic activities, and social responsibility projects throughout the year. Students can join clubs in theater, music, dance, photography, and more for personal development.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">On-campus social spaces allow students to enjoy their free time with cafeterias, gyms, and relaxation areas enhancing campus life. Ankara&#8217;s rich cultural and artistic scene further enriches the student experience.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Students can attend various events in museums, theaters, and concert halls across the city. The university encourages student engagement through club activities and supports social participation. </p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Cultural Adaptation for International Student</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">With its multicultural student body, the university offers several support services to help international students adapt to life in Turkey and on campus. The International Relations Coordination Office guides new students through registration, course selection, and <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/uzun-donem-ikamet-izni-avantajlari/" data-type="post" data-id="4025">residence permit</a> procedures.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Being located in Ankara offers a cultural advantage with the city’s diverse and dynamic environment, helping international students adjust quickly. Active student clubs support integration through social and cultural events.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Intercultural events, orientation days, and language exchange groups promote interaction among students from different backgrounds. This helps foster a multicultural campus environment where students can experience Turkish culture and share their own heritage.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Health Services and Security</h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1279" height="720" src="https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/orig.jpg" alt="Image" class="wp-image-10941" srcset="https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/orig.jpg 1279w, https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/orig-300x169.jpg 300w, https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/orig-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/orig-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1279px) 100vw, 1279px" /></figure>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university prioritizes students&#8217; health and safety. On-campus health units provide basic medical services, and students are referred to public or private hospitals in Ankara for more comprehensive care.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">International students can access public healthcare services at low cost through the General Health Insurance (GSS) system. The International Relations Office provides guidance on health insurance and access to medical services.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Campus security is maintained 24/7, with security personnel at entry points and surveillance systems throughout. Ankara is considered one of Turkey’s safest cities, offering a secure living environment for international students.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Transportation</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university is centrally located with excellent public transportation access. Campuses are easily reachable via buses, minibuses, metro, and Ankaray. Students benefit from discounted transportation using the AnkaraKart.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The nearby Kızılay metro station offers quick city access. Public transport connects campuses to downtown and other universities easily, with Ankara’s broad transport network being a major benefit for students.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Major transport hubs like Esenboğa Airport, AŞTİ Bus Terminal, and the High-Speed Train Station offer convenient intercity and international travel. The university’s central location facilitates both local and long-distance commuting.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Student Support Services</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">To support students academically and socially, the university offers a wide range of services. The International Relations Office assists with registration, visa applications, residence permits, and health insurance for international students.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Psychological Counseling and Guidance Center provides free support for emotional and social well-being, helping with stress, exam anxiety, adaptation issues, and personal development.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Career Center supports students with career planning, internships, job searches, and CV preparation. Events like job fairs and industry meet-ups help students transition to the professional world.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Academic advisory services guide students throughout their education from course selection to graduation helping them build a strong academic foundation and succeed in university life.</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-10-31T10:44:12Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2025-10-31T10:44:12Z' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'ankara-haci-bayram-veli-university';
