to Study in Turkey","publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/alanya-alaaddin-keykubat-university.webp","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/alanya-alaaddin-keykubat-university.webp","width":"1024","height":"576","inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/alanya-alaaddin-keykubat-university/#webpage","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/alanya-alaaddin-keykubat-university/","name":"Alanya Alaaddin Keykubat University - RoadtoStudy","datePublished":"2025-10-30T14:19:42+03:00","dateModified":"2025-10-30T14:19:43+03:00","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website"},"primaryImageOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/alanya-alaaddin-keykubat-university.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/busra/","name":"busra","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/busra/","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a3c0f700b03ed22f8ab3a40880c2b539035a9a6e21bb16550f65e22a0ff39809?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a3c0f700b03ed22f8ab3a40880c2b539035a9a6e21bb16550f65e22a0ff39809?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","caption":"busra","inLanguage":"en-US"}},{"@type":"Article","headline":"Alanya Alaaddin Keykubat University - RoadtoStudy","keywords":"Alanya Alaaddin Keykubat","datePublished":"2025-10-30T14:19:42+03:00","dateModified":"2025-10-30T14:19:43+03:00","author":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/busra/","name":"busra"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"description":"Established in 2015, Alanya Alaaddin Keykubat University is a public university located in Alanya, a district of Antalya, Turkey. Despite being a young","name":"Alanya Alaaddin Keykubat University - RoadtoStudy","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/alanya-alaaddin-keykubat-university/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/alanya-alaaddin-keykubat-university/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/alanya-alaaddin-keykubat-university.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/alanya-alaaddin-keykubat-university/#webpage"}}]}]}'), '$.content_html', '<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Alanya Alaaddin Keykubat University: History and Vision</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Established in 2015, <a href="https://alanya.edu.tr" data-type="link" data-id="https://alanya.edu.tr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Alanya Alaaddin Keykubat University</a> is a public university located in Alanya, a district of Antalya, Turkey. Despite being a young institution, it has rapidly grown in academic structure and expanded its range of programs. Named after Sultan Alaaddin Keykubat I of the Anatolian Seljuk Empire, the university reflects a commitment to historical heritage and modern education.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university’s main vision is to train entrepreneurial and innovative individuals who are recognized internationally in scientific, cultural, and social fields. It aims to integrate the Mediterranean region’s tourism, health, and agriculture potential into its academic framework, placing strong emphasis on applied education. It also strives to be among the universities contributing to regional development.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The institution stands out with its student-centered approach, its encouragement of interdisciplinary studies, and its focus on R&amp;D. With rapidly developing academic units and a young, dynamic staff, the university continues to attract students both nationally and internationally.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Education</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Alanya Alaaddin Keykubat University offers a broad academic spectrum through its various faculties and applied learning approach. It houses faculties such as Medicine, Engineering, Education, Business, and Tourism. Programs are designed based on regional needs and international academic standards.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The primary language of instruction is Turkish, though some departments offer English-supported education. International students can attend Turkish preparatory classes. Erasmus+ and Mevlana exchange programs offer educational opportunities in Europe and other countries.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Thanks to Alanya’s strong tourism identity, applied education is especially emphasized in tourism, healthcare, and service-related sectors. The academic staff includes faculty members with both national and international experience. Students are supported in research and project development through mentoring.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Campus and Technological Infrastructure</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university campus is located close to the Alanya city center, in a natural setting. The main campus includes modern classrooms, conference halls, laboratories, research centers, and a digital library. Students benefit from the technological infrastructure in their coursework and projects.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Remote learning systems, e-library resources, and digital automation platforms enable students to manage their academic processes online. The campus offers high-speed internet and digital information systems throughout.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Specialized labs and training areas support practical education in fields like health and sports sciences. Cafeterias, open spaces, and recreational zones are designed to meet students’ social and personal needs.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Accommodation</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Alanya Alaaddin Keykubat University offers both public and private housing options for students. State-run KYK dormitories provide economical, safe, and comfortable living spaces. Rooms typically accommodate 3–4 students and include dining halls, study rooms, and laundry facilities.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Private dorms and apartment rentals near the university are also popular choices. The university’s International Relations Office supports international students during the accommodation process.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Student dormitories emphasize safety, cleanliness, and social interaction. Shared spaces foster community, while quiet and organized environments allow for academic focus.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Social Life</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Alanya, one of the Mediterranean’s top tourist destinations, is also an appealing city for student life. The university leverages this advantage to offer a vibrant campus life filled with cultural, athletic, and social activities. Numerous student clubs, arts societies, and sports teams are active within the university.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Throughout the year, festivals, concerts, symposiums, and competitions allow students to enjoy themselves while developing personally. Alanya’s beaches, historical landmarks, and nature trails provide ideal weekend getaways for students.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Cultural Integration for International Students</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Alanya Alaaddin Keykubat University offers an inclusive and supportive academic environment for students from various parts of the world. Its International Relations Office organizes orientation programs each semester for newly enrolled international students. These sessions provide details about life in Turkey, university regulations, local transportation, and <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/kulturel-farkliliklar-anlasmazlik/">cultural differences</a>.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Alanya’s multicultural atmosphere, shaped by its tourism-based identity, helps international students integrate smoothly into the city and university life. Events such as “International Culture Days” allow students to showcase their own cultures and experience Turkish traditions.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Social activities, student club involvement, and community projects throughout the academic year help international students quickly adapt to campus life. Alanya’s welcoming environment minimizes feelings of social isolation and supports student well-being.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Health Services and Security</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The campus features a basic health unit offering primary healthcare services. Additionally, Alanya is home to a well-equipped state hospital and several private healthcare institutions. International students can access Turkey’s General Health Insurance (GSS) system during their stay, ensuring comprehensive healthcare coverage.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Alanya is considered one of Turkey’s safest cities. The university campus and surrounding dormitory areas are secured 24/7 by security personnel, surveillance cameras, and entry control systems.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university provides guidance and support in case of health issues, accidents, or emergencies. Psychological counseling services are also available, offered confidentially to help students maintain emotional well-being.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Transportation</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university campus is conveniently located near the city center, making it accessible on foot or via short public transport rides. Public buses and minibuses operate frequently across Alanya, offering affordable transportation for students.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Student transportation cards offer discounted fares. Since the campus is close to dormitories and social areas, daily life is very manageable. Alanya’s southern coastal location also ensures easy access to other tourist cities.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Gazipaşa-Alanya Airport is about 40 minutes from the campus, and there are regular shuttle services to Antalya Airport as well. Both domestic and international travel are easily managed.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Student Support Services</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Alanya Alaaddin Keykubat University offers a variety of services to support students’ academic and personal development. The International Relations Office provides one-on-one guidance for international students on registration, residence permits, health insurance, and visas—ensuring a smooth transition through administrative processes.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The academic advising system helps students with course selection, program content, and exams. The university’s Psychological Counseling Unit offers free, confidential support.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Career Development Center provides guidance on internships, volunteering, CV preparation, and interview simulations. Seminars and workshops prepare students for life after graduation.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-10-30T11:19:42Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2025-10-30T11:19:43Z') WHERE "collection" = 'pages' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_pages" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'alanya-alaaddin-keykubat-university' );
