://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/afyonkarahisar-saglik-bilimleri-university/#webpage","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/afyonkarahisar-saglik-bilimleri-university/","name":"Afyonkarahisar Sağlık Bilimleri University - RoadtoStudy","datePublished":"2025-10-27T13:30:57+03:00","dateModified":"2025-10-27T13:30:58+03:00","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/busra/","name":"busra","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/busra/","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a3c0f700b03ed22f8ab3a40880c2b539035a9a6e21bb16550f65e22a0ff39809?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a3c0f700b03ed22f8ab3a40880c2b539035a9a6e21bb16550f65e22a0ff39809?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","caption":"busra","inLanguage":"en-US"}},{"@type":"Article","headline":"Afyonkarahisar Sağlık Bilimleri University - RoadtoStudy","keywords":"Afyonkarahisar Sağlık Bilimleri","datePublished":"2025-10-27T13:30:57+03:00","dateModified":"2025-10-27T13:30:58+03:00","author":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/busra/","name":"busra"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"description":"Afyonkarahisar Sağlık Bilimleri University (AFSU) is a public university located in western Turkey, in the city of Afyonkarahisar, renowned for its thermal","name":"Afyonkarahisar Sağlık Bilimleri University - RoadtoStudy","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/afyonkarahisar-saglik-bilimleri-university/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/afyonkarahisar-saglik-bilimleri-university/#webpage"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/afyonkarahisar-saglik-bilimleri-university/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Afyonkarahisar Health Sciences University (AFSU)</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Afyonkarahisar Sağlık Bilimleri University (AFSU) is a public university located in western Turkey, in the city of Afyonkarahisar, renowned for its thermal tourism. Specializing in health sciences, AFSU offers prospective students a strong academic foundation, a modern campus, and a learning environment enriched by the region’s natural resources. This guide provides an overview of the university, from its history to campus life.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">History and Vision</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">AFSU was established on May 18, 2018, under Law No. 7141, published in Official Gazette No. 30425. Formed by separating the health-related faculties from Afyon Kocatepe University, AFSU now operates as an independent institution fully dedicated to health education. Its founding and current rector is Prof. Dr. Nurullah Okumuş (as of March 19, 2025; for updates, please refer to official sources).</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">AFSU’s vision is to become one of Turkey’s leading centers in health sciences and technologies. Its mission is to contribute to national and regional health by training qualified health professionals. The university aims to stand out through research in medical sciences and thermal health tourism.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Education</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">AFSU has a health-focused academic structure, including four faculties: Medicine, Dentistry, Pharmacy, and Health Sciences. It also includes three vocational schools (Atatürk, Bolvadin, Şuhut) and a Graduate School. As of 2025, AFSU offers 11 undergraduate and 22 associate degree programs. Approximately 600 academic staff (including 43 professors, 49 associate professors, and 159 PhDs) support education with modern laboratories.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Central Research Laboratory is equipped for thermal therapy and pharmacological studies. According to YÖK Atlas, 6,736 students were enrolled in 2021–2022, with numbers changing annually. AFSU participates in Erasmus+ and Farabi programs, providing national and international opportunities. For more information, refer to AFSU’s official resources.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Campus and Technological Infrastructure</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The main campus, Zafer Health Complex, is located in Dörtyol Neighborhood. It includes modern classrooms, labs, and a library. The Health Practice and Research Center features thermal treatment pools and rehabilitation units. Technological infrastructure includes simulation rooms, smart classrooms, and a digital library.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The campus library offers nearly 40,000 printed materials and access to databases like EBSCO. Eco-friendly practices support campus sustainability. With its thermal resources, the campus provides a unique learning environment for prospective students.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Dormitories</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">AFSU collaborates with nearby KYK dormitories, which are affordable and secure. These facilities offer dining halls, internet access, and study areas. The university provides guidance to help students settle into city life. Private dormitories and rental housing are also available. Students can apply for KYK housing after admission. The campus’s central location makes accommodation options easily accessible.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Social Life</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://www.afsu.edu.tr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AFSU</a> offers students an active campus life. Over 20 student clubs support cultural and professional development. Sports facilities are available for basketball, volleyball, and fitness. The university organizes spring festivals, seminars, and exhibitions.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Nearby attractions such as Sandıklı Thermal Springs, Phrygian Valley, and Afyon Castle add cultural and recreational value. Students can enjoy a peaceful experience both on campus and in the city.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Cultural Integration for International Students</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">AFSU welcomes international students. Language courses and orientation programs support <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/turkiyede-kulturel-uyum/">cultural adaptation</a>. The Erasmus+ program promotes global mobility, and campus events encourage multicultural interaction. Afyonkarahisar’s friendly atmosphere offers a warm welcome to international students. The “Barrier-Free AFSU” unit ensures equal opportunities for students with disabilities.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Health Services and Security</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The on-campus Health Center provides basic medical services. The Health Practice and Research Center offers tertiary healthcare services. The Psychological Counseling Unit provides mental health support. Campus safety is ensured with 24/7 surveillance and security staff. Emergency teams are always ready. Thermal therapies also support overall health and wellness.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Transportation</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university is located 5 km from Afyonkarahisar city center and is easily accessible via public buses and minibuses. Afyonkarahisar Airport is 60 km away, and the bus terminal is 10 km away. The university also offers shuttle services. The flat terrain of the city makes access convenient. Prospective students can benefit from a well-planned transportation system.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Student Support Services</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">AFSU supports students through its Career Center, which provides guidance on internships and job opportunities. Financial aid is available through KYK scholarships and loans. The Barrier-Free AFSU unit offers accessibility services for students with disabilities. Academic advising and mentoring programs help guide students throughout their university journey. Prospective students can prepare for their future with the help of these resources</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-10-27T10:30:57Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2025-10-27T10:30:58Z' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'afyonkarahisar-saglik-bilimleri-university';
